              {
                "type": "CHANGED",
                "text": "Changed most interactions with TMI.js."
              },
              {
                "type": "COMMENT",
                "text": "A lot of Changes to TMI.js (and my understanding of it) changed many little things! Mostly to reduce redundancy and improve reliability and consistancy."
              },
              {
                "type": "CHANGED",
                "detailed": true,
                "text": "Connect is now async and returns the Promise from TMI.js Connect Function"
              },
              {
                "type": "ADDED",
                "text": "Added say(message: String, channel: String) / saySync(...)"
              },
              {
                "type": "ADDED",
                "text": "Added timeout(username: String, length: Integer, reason: String, channel: String) / timeoutSync(...)"
              },
              {
                "type": "ADDED",
                "text": "Added ban(username: String, reason: String, channel: String) / banSync(...)"
              },
              {
                "type": "ADDED",
                "text": "Added deleteMessage(id: String, channel: String) / deleteMessageSync(...)"
              },
              {
                "type": "ADDED",
                "text": "Added readyState() -> using TMI.js Functions"
              },
              {
